<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَدْلَى دَلْوَهُ}</span> ... فَأَرْسَلَ دَلْوَهُ فِي البِئْرِ؛ لِيَمْلَأَهَا بِالمَاءِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَسَرُّوهُ بِضَاعَةً}</span> ... كَتَمَ إِخْوَةُ يُوسُفَ كَوْنَهُ أَخَاهُمْ لِيَبِيعُوهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَرَوْهُ}</span> ... بَاعَهُ إِخْوَتُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَخْسٍ}</span> ... قَلِيلٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَثْوَاهُ}</span> ... مَقَامَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَشُدَّهُ}</span> ... مُنْتَهَى قُوَّتِهِ فِي شَبَابِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَاوَدَتْهُ}</span> ... دَعَتْهُ إِلَى نَفْسِهَا بِرِفْقٍ وَلِينٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَيْتَ لَكَ}</span> ... هَلُمَّ إِلَيَّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَعَاذَ اللهِ}</span> ... أَعْتَصِمُ بِاللهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَبِّي}</span> ... سَيِّدِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَثْوَايَ}</span> ... مَنْزِلِي وَمُقَامِي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَمَّتْ بِهِ}</span> ... مَالَتْ نَفْسُهَا لِفِعْلِ الفَاحِشَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَهَمَّ بِهَا}</span> ... خَطَرَ بِقَلْبِهِ إِجَابَتُهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُرْهَانَ رَبِّهِ}</span> ... آيَةً مِنَ اللهِ زَجَرَتْهُ عَنْ ذَلِكَ الخَاطِرِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخْلَصِينَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ أَخْلَصُوا فِي عِبَادَةِ اللهِ؛ فَأَخْلَصَهُمْ، وَاخْتَصَّهُمْ بِرَحْمَتِهِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاسُتَبَقَا الْبَابَ}</span> ... أَسْرَعَا إِلَى البَابِ يُرِيدُ الخُرُوجَ وَهِيَ تَمْنَعُهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
